{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The messages within a transaction carry the cumulative values of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a field. In case one or more messages within a transaction are not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"received by the Server (e.g., as a result of radio collisions),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the next received message will make up for the lost messages,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"carrying cumulative values of the field.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A new transaction is started when this field is set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or when the last message of the transaction was sent 6 or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"more seconds earlier.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This defaults to "},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", which means that each new message will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive a new transaction identifier (if not set explicitly)."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightLCLightOnOffSetUnacknowledged\/continueTransaction","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lightlclightonoffsetu